videos.headline: Georgia Tech ties game off Marshall's 67-yard TD
videos.description: Georgia Tech's Marcus Marshall takes the handoff and flies by Virginia's defense, taking the ball 67 yards to the house.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech takes the lead with 54-yard TD
videos.description: Georgia Tech QB Justin Thomas connects with RB Clinton Lynch for an easy TD to take a 14-10 lead over Virginia.

videos.headline: Virginia's lands crucial TD catch
videos.description: Virginia's Matt Johns connects with Ryan Santoro on 4th-and-goal for a crucial touchdown to cut Georgia Tech's lead to 24-16.

videos.headline: Yellow Jackets pick off Virginia for TD
videos.description: Georgia Tech extends its lead to 31-17 over Virginia with a 24-yard pick-six.
